00:32:43,763 --> 00:32:45,513
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">This <i>is</i> a date.</font>

146
00:32:48,343 --> 00:32:49,243
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Shall we go?</font>

147
00:33:17,843 --> 00:33:18,723
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Here you go.</font>

148
00:33:38,733 --> 00:33:39,913
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Weird.</font>

149
00:34:46,433 --> 00:34:49,353
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Wow, that was so weird!</font>

150
00:34:49,353 --> 00:34:51,663
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Everyone went all out with their disguises, didn't they?</font>

151
00:34:51,663 --> 00:34:53,743
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">It was like a mimicking competition!</font>

152
00:34:53,743 --> 00:34:55,163
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Is it like this every year?</font>

153
00:34:55,483 --> 00:34:59,833
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Yeah, every time summer comes around...</font>

154
00:35:08,683 --> 00:35:14,083
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">When I'm away from you, even though I can't be around crowds, I want to go see you.</font>

155
00:35:39,273 --> 00:35:40,193
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">That mask...</font>

156
00:35:41,103 --> 00:35:41,893
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Have it.</font>

157
00:35:48,603 --> 00:35:55,133
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>He probably won't come to that place next summer.</i></font>

158
00:35:57,563 --> 00:36:00,883
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>This is definitely our last...</i></font>

159
00:36:21,933 --> 00:36:22,783
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin?</font>

160
00:36:33,903 --> 00:36:34,713
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin!</font>

161
00:37:24,133 --> 00:37:25,443
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">I love you, too.</font>

162
00:37:59,703 --> 00:38:03,563
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">We wanted to be with Gin forever, but...</font>

163
00:38:03,563 --> 00:38:08,803
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">Gin wanted to touch a human.</font>

164
00:38:14,063 --> 00:38:16,383
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>I probably won't be able to</i></font>

165
00:38:43,143 --> 00:38:44,933
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>So, let's go.</i></font>

166
00:38:49,823 --> 00:38:50,993
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1"><i>Let us go.</i></font>

167
00:39:49,943 --> 00:39:55,873
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}<font face="Goodfish">The cicadas laugh out in song</font></font>

168
00:40:10,613 --> 00:40:16,903
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}but I promised to come here again tomorrow</font>

169
00:40:20,653 --> 00:40:32,933
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer is in full bloom</font>

170
00:41:01,973 --> 00:41:08,243
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}I thought the tale would never end</font>

171
00:41:34,223 --> 00:41:46,763
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer flies by</font>

172
00:41:48,333 --> 00:42:01,233
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to hide away its treasures till next year</font>

173
00:42:49,143 --> 00:42:55,583
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}I'll never ever forget</font>

174
00:42:56,863 --> 00:43:03,063
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}those golden summer days</font>

175
00:43:03,733 --> 00:43:10,613
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}That summer which brought joy</font>

176
00:43:11,903 --> 00:43:18,193
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to my boring everyday life</font>

177
00:43:37,803 --> 00:43:50,093
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}to help me keep my promise of that day</font>

178
00:43:51,313 --> 00:44:04,073
<font face="Goodfish" size="80" color="#f9f4f1">{\an3}The summer is still in bloom</font>

